    dc:creator "Jiao, Ke-Long; Zhou, Xiao-Yi; Wang, Hao; Fu, Huai-Jun; Zhou, Da-Kang; Li, Jing-Bo; Xiong, De-Ping; Wang, Yuan-Hong; Bu, Wen-Jun; Kolesik, Peter" ;
    dc:date "2020" ;
    dc:title "A new genus and species of gall midge (Diptera: Cecidomyiidae) inducing leaf galls on Peking lilac, Syringa reticulata subsp. pekinensis (Oleaceae), in China" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3674437>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3674441>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3674439> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3674437>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–7. Pekinomyia syringae. Male. (1) 3rd flagellomere, (2) fore tarsal claw with empodium, (3) palpus, (4) wing, (5) gonostylus, ventral, (6) terminalia, dorsal, (7) terminalia, ventral. Scale bars 0.1 mm in 1, 3, 5, 6; 0.05 mm in 2; 0.5 mm in 4." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3674437/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3674441>
    dc:description "FIGURES 16–19. Infestation of Syringa reticulata subsp. pekinensis by Pekinomyia syringae. (16) females laying eggs on young leaves, note large number of orange eggs, (17) male resting on leaf, (18) leaf galls, (19) infested leaves, note large number of leaves fallen off to the ground prematurely." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3674441/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3674439>
    dc:description "FIGURES 8–15. Pekinomyia syringae. 8–11: female, 12–14: larva, 15: pupa. (8) 3rd flagellomere, ventral, (9) 3rd flagellomere, dorsal, (10) postabdomen from 8th segment, dorsal, (11) postabdomen from 7th segment, lateral, (12) head, dorsal, (13) sternal spatula with adjacent papillae, (14) last two abdominal segments, dorsal, (15) head, ventral. Scale bars 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3674439/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

